msgid ""
"For shorthand TensorMesh aliases ``phi := shape_val``, ``gradphi := "
"shape_grad``, ``J := jacobian``, ``G := jacobian``, ``GxW := JxW`` — "
"useful when transcribing weak forms directly from the math."
